directions: Using a mixer, beat the cream cheese until smooth and creamy. Add in ranch dressing packet and mix to combine. Continue mixing and slowly add in the beer. Stir in shredded cheese.
Spread dip mixture into a small casserole dish and bake for 30 minutes or until the dip is heated through.
ingredients: Pretzels, chips, or crackers for dipping
title: Warm Beer Cheese Dip
